OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain will soon clear east then
OL,6,Fsunny spells and showers. Drier for a
OL,7,Ftime in the afternoon before further
OL,8,Fshowers later, heavy at times. Cool
OL,9,Fand blustery.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FSunny then clear spells and
OL,12,Fscattered showers in the evening.
OL,13,FLargely dry but cloudy overnight but
OL,14,Fchance of the odd spot of rain. Patchy
OL,15,Ffrost in places.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FIt will be quite cool with
OL,18,Fbright or sunny spells and scattered
OL,19,Fheavy showers. Chance of overnight
OL,20,Ffrost in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
