OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FRather cold and blustery Thursday with
OL,7,Fscattered heavy showers, chance of
OL,8,Fovernight frost. A few early showers
OL,9,Fon Friday, otherwise dry with sunny
OL,10,Fspells. Mostly dry and bright Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
